      <item>
        <title>Question about ice ward</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[Vandalay]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <aside class="quote no-group" data-username="RopeStringFace" data-post="3" data-topic="14139">
<div class="title">
<div class="quote-controls"></div>
<img alt="" width="20" height="20" src="https://forum.throneoflies.com/user_avatar/forum.throneoflies.com/ropestringface/40/1106_2.png" class="avatar"> RopeStringFace:</div>
<blockquote>
<p>Player A ice wards player Z, player B occupied player A, player C assassinates player Z</p>
</blockquote>
</aside>
<p>I don’t believe it’s an “order of events” rather than a “this ability counteracts that ability”.</p>
<p>If you were going for some kind of realism kind of thing, just think of it as if all actions were going on in a full hour. IE butler is giving drinks to CW 1, when a wall blocks him out 10 minutes in, freeing up the CW to spend the second 50 minutes putting up a wall, and the assasain comes in during the last 5 minutes of the hour to try and perform the assasination, but is stopped by the wall that was up.</p>
          <p><a href="https://forum.throneoflies.com/t/question-about-ice-ward/14139/4">Read full topic</a></p>
        ]]></description>
